title: Star Wars Galaxies + Jump To Lightspeed + Patches and Updates 1-
description:
The original Star Wars Galaxies 3x ISO CDs, plus the Jump to Light Speed ISO CD.

Includes the TRE patches and update 1-59 from the 8+ years of the game, plus TRE Explorer to view the patch files. Space ships, armor, weapons, races, housing, harvesters, planet maps, terrains, vehicles, sound effects, music and more. Original CDs were about 2GB, but the additional content from the patches and update adds over 6GB of data for a total of 8+ GB.

Star Wars Galaxies closed Dec. 15th 2011 and cannot be played via Sony Online although private emulators exist.
